				<td colspan="2"><span>Ok, this is just theory  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" /> so no flamming allowed.
<br />
If u have semi decent gear, possibly a SS bp and some FT maybe you could throw on 4 dots and then charm Eldrige. Since he likes to cast a few times in a row you sould be able to get off all 4 dots b4 he kills u with melee. Then charm him and let the dots hurt him untill they wear off. Heal up and break charm. Rinse and repeat till he is dead. Maybe just chant kite till you get kinda low on hp 40% or so, charm, and heal. My guess is that this will take awhile and it's not the best way to do it but...its a way.
<br />

<br />
P.S. or you could do what i did...go get a bunch of the gnashers (spermies) and charm Eldrige and use swarm to kill. You have AE fear so b4 u break charm run up and fear all the gnashers b4 u do so only he hits u when he summons.</span></td>
